# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  Catholic Church of the Lord's Baptism — .gitignore
#  Keeps secrets, personal data, and junk OUT of the repository.
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# --- Secrets & environment files (NEVER commit these) ---
.env
.env.*
*.local
secrets.json
secrets.*.json
credentials*.json
service-account*.json
*.pem
*.key
*.p12

# --- Parishioner / member data (keep ALL personal data out of git) ---
# Member lists, family records, and giving exports belong in your
# database (e.g. Google Sheets) — never in this public-facing repo.
members*.csv
parishioners*.csv
*-members.csv
*-export.csv
donations*.csv
giving*.csv
*-backup.csv

# --- Node / build tooling (only relevant if you ever add a build step) ---
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.npm/
.cache/
dist/
build/

# --- Netlify CLI local state ---
.netlify/

# --- Editors / IDEs ---
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.history/

# --- Operating-system junk ---
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
desktop.ini

# --- Logs & temp ---
*.log
tmp/
*.tmp
